Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, your bath's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sawako, how's school been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:30.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always says it's fun, but she really looks like she's gleeful this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:33.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gleeful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako... my Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:43.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Dad, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:53.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to forget what I used to be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:02:02.76,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what he meant, but I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:09.29,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm using up my lifetime's supply of happiness right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:13.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm happy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:23.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida? The thin-eyed girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:27.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to be a real problem in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made her teacher cry and beat up all the guys in her class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:34.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a lot worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my eyes aren't {\i1}that{\i0}{\fscx50} {\fscx100} thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:45.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred guys in middle school... that's just crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:48.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying there are a hundred guys that could satisfy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hook me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:52.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know what they're like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, my legend was way grander than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:02.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my eyes aren't that thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}are{\i0}{\fscx50} {\fscx100} thinner than you think, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:06.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies. All lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the rumors about Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you who told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's saying so,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:39.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she's using Kazehaya and you two to up her status.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna ask just to be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:55.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Yano-san, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I beat up all the guys in my class huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:07.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm a slut, and I did a hundred guys in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:22.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida-san, if it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:24.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a summary for the midterm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you would have a use for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure white!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:44.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to rent some horror story videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please give me some recommendations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure white!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yoshida,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I copy that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:56.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I'll give you some scrubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:00.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:06.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like being helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple pure white!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:24.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously saw him last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:29.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin, I really want to go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was drinking last night…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:43.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of them. Running around my glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Round and round, round and round.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:50.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then one by one they went into my glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some tough bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:03.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's that Kuronuma girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:10.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All sorts of weird stuff has been happening since I looked into her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:14.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sit next to her, you must know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she cursed or—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe what I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:24.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kuronuma I see is pure-hearted and good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... are you going out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you getting all red about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're not really—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:46.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.25,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He really has a type, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin was talking to me about little old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:07.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:08.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.62,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,His bangs are standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's normal, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:17.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,After I talked about having her to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:22.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,His bangs... I want to see his bangs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I can't look at her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:32.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,His bangs... too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:43.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,In my happiness, my heart's racing faster day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what everyone else is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they like being with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:00.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:07.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was normal not to have anyone around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.96,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I never even thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:26.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, I've been filled with feelings that I'd never known before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have them close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:34.10,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like presents that I've received for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:46.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor going around lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:47.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It keeps getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:56.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying you beat an elderly man to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:01.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did help up an old guy after he fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that Yano-san is involved in paid dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't believe it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:15.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently that rumor's coming from Kuronuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:23.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sort of worried... why would there be such a rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a horrible rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think people are even more afraid of me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shino-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:42.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:49.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some serious rumors going around these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:55.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Shino-chan heard the rumors about the psychic aura and curses and all that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:01.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think misunderstandings go away that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misunderstandings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:11.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, Sadako would never spread rumors about her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't bother me as much as it used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around me is so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:21.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you've loosened up, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone talking about Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:32.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the three of us are notorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand the rumors about us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the rumors about Sadako are different from the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:41.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you made some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:00.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:01.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:07.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship is like what's between Yano-san and Yoshida-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:14.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really get the sense that they care for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:18.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't think I deserve to be called a friend yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:26.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I care for the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:31.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I really hope I'll be able to call them friends someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Top secret practice menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:45.80,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:51.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:02.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't asked her what she meant by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:10.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, we might not be friends with her per se.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not laughing like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:25.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, can you come sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sort of bummed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk about something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:45.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I—we both like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:49.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:03.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:27.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they understand? With so little?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,We like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:37.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:43.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yano-san and Yoshida-san don't look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:47.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel happy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's something I can do to cheer them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:56.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she got all cocky and got Yano and Yoshida to back her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:58.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,To back her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:02.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's even using Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0}{\fscx50} {\fscx100} Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First I was Sadako, now I'm a gang leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those black rumors about Yano and Yoshida are really something though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:25.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Backing me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they were down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:34.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sadako's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she's wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:44.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's going to become seriously worthless too, if he keeps getting followed around by Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:15:01.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san are just kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:05.47,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're approaching me in kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.47,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:11.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she's wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:17.22,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I hurting people by being around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:25.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to hurt Kazehaya-kun the way I hurt Yano-san and Yoshida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear the story about the little old men?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've seen them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:32.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked just like Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're shitting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I not be around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I not be around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, you look like you cried yourself to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you stayed up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:33.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think Sadako spread those rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially after what she said yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:48.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, she doesn't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:51.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked if she liked us, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:59.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't have been the one to spread rumors about us if she said she did like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you hoped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:11.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally believed she wouldn't spread rumors about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:16.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm worried; what if she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that she wouldn't spread rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:25.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself for thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their eyes are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:44.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:49.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I upset you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:55.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:57.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:05.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean, she upset us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, did she really spread those rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:17.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:20.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's sorry that she doesn't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, this sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:28.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was being stuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:33.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a pretty big part of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:37.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally thought she liked me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:43.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're more hurt than I thought they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.98,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find the people spreading the rumors and set the record straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:54.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-san and Yoshida-san aren't backing me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:58.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell them that they're just really kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.57,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to fix misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:07.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:17.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to be happy and laughing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.44,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the other two that want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:36.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:38.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:45.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:48.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you crying earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:52.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:57.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something to hurt you? To make you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:02.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, you didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:15.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I would never hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:19.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:30.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:39.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He never avoided me, no matter what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:45.12,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I cause him trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I cause him trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to avoid him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:54.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to stay by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:02.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it right to avoid him? Is it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people I care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:31.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I can do right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:34.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:36.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
